        "* We designed a machine learning model: we defined the features it has and how it converts them into predictions. We also defined the parameters of the model ‚Äì the weights that we can change to tune the model to the data.\n",
        "* We then rewrote the model as a formula and developed a training algorithm that uses formula optimization to find the best weights."
